# ==========================================
# Q7: Product Management (JWT RBAC)
# ==========================================

### Login as Admin
POST http://localhost:6007/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "role": "admin"
}

### Add Product (Requires Admin Token)
POST http://localhost:6007/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

{
    "name": "MacBook Pro M3",
    "price": 2500
}


